rows.name: My Nopon friend invited me once!

rows.label: qst202706_msg0003
rows.name:
They said everyone forms a circle
and chants spells while lying down.

rows.label: qst202706_msg0004
rows.name: They call it the Purpure Altar.

rows.label: qst202706_msg0005
rows.name:
It sounded cool and fun, but
since I'm not a Nopon, the
leader wouldn't let me join...[ML:Dash ]
